  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Correlations between the eigenvalues of a random matrix</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Exact analytical expressions are found for the joint probability distribution functions of n eigenvalues belonging to a random Hermitian matrix of order $N$, where $n$ is any integer and $N\to \infty$. The distribution functions, like those obtained earlier for $n = 2$, involve only trigonometrical functions of the eigenvalue differences.</subfield>
